<h3 id="tools">Tools</h3>
<p>One of my tenets is that &lt;a class=’internal-link’ href=’/Tools%20don’t%20matter/’&gt;tools don’t matter&lt;/a&gt;. The only thing that matters about a tool is that it must allow me to manipulate plain text or Markdown files that exist in a folder that I can move around freely. I once learned that</p>

<p>I don’t enjoy having to export things out of my system every time I change tools.</p>
